s://talkwithwebvisitors.com to try Talk With Web Visitor now.\r\n\r\nIf you\'d like to unsubscribe click here http://talkwithwebvisitors.com/unsubscribe.aspx?d=thezouple.com', 'There they goâ¦', '2021-02-11', 'ac1AOlixD0HTkRlXc2PytQgae3IY183mUkx82qa8', '2021-02-11 05:29:18', '2021-02-11 05:29:18'),
