r\n\r\nYou could be converting up to 100X more leads today!\r\nEric\r\n\r\nPS: Talk With Web Visitor offers a FREE 14 days trial â and it even includes International Long Distance Calling. \r\nYou have customers waiting to talk with you right nowâ¦ donât keep them waiting. \r\nCLICK HERE http://talkwithcustomer.com to try Talk With Web Visitor now.\r\n\r\nIf you\'d like to unsubscribe click here http://talkwithcustomer.com/unsubscribe.aspx?d=thezouple.com', 'Cool website!', '2021-07-14', 'nWt3piO21zBwP72GfskhKjKfevMaZ6UdK5dbMStH', '2021-07-14 00:56:37', '2021-07-14 00:56:37');
