(1, 'Customize Shirt in less then 5 Minutes', '5f40e1db0613eWe Built for Satisfaction.png', '<p>It has been our long experience in the field of Men&#39;s standard sizes shirt with fixed styles. The main reason behind the starting of customization of shirts is that styles could no more&nbsp;be a limitation of your choices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zouple Shirts are made up of finest fabrics/cotton, and we are not going to decide your choice of pattern. It is you who will decide it, select it &amp; we will give a shape&nbsp;it for you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is beyond customization because inspite of our customize shirt patterns, you can also tell us regarding your choice which is not listed in our styles by just dropping a mail to us of your choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>so &quot;Go Ahead With Confidence&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><kbd><span dir=\"ltr\"><cite><strong>Click Below to Explore more &gt;</strong></cite></span></kbd></p>', 'RT2ZgB8SsxonBiX5n1gpZrjsdjhXaLN433S5pr9p', '2019-09-30 12:17:22', '2020-08-22 09:14:03');
