(7, 'embroidered-genuine-leather-shoulder-slingtote-bag-leb0003', 0, '[\"2\",\"8\"]', 3, 'HLB-ICB-LeB0003', 'Embroidered Genuine Leather shoulder Sling/Tote Bag [LeB0003]', '18', '3', '5d722e68de453IMG_0010.JPG', '[\"5d722e68debb9IMG_0003 (2).jpg\",\"5d722e68df23fIMG_0004 (2).jpg\",\"5d722e68df5efIMG_0005 (2).jpg\",\"5d722e68df936IMG_0006.JPG\",\"5d722e68dffa8IMG_0007.JPG\",\"5d722e68e055bIMG_0008 (2).jpg\",\"5d722e68e0857IMG_0012.JPG\"]', '<p>The bag is perfect in workmanship. The elegant design can show your beautiful temperament.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More humanized design for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is very suitable for Wedding , party, ball, daily casual wearing, travel, office occasion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Great present for your friend,your family or yourself.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand Name: </strong>Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: HLB-JAG-LeB0003</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gender:</strong> Female</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong> Genuine Leather.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design Work:</strong> Ambroidery Work with Two compartments inside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Measurement(Approx): </strong>37 CM Wide, 27 CM Tall, 10 CM Width.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lining: </strong>Fine quality Polyster</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The bag is clean inside and out and sanitized before dispatching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Leather Bag with Ambroidery Work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coin Pocket is provided in each compartment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ideal for carrying Tablet, Mobile and daily use accessories.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Leather Bag with Ambroidery Work', 'Leather Bag with Ambroidery Work', 'Leather Bag with Ambroidery Work', '30ePZJffw2ZKVLsK2zpfk5DWp6zacN3GrwkFQkRs', '2019-09-25 10:09:49', '2019-09-06 06:25:30'),
