 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Premium Embroidered Genuine Leather Tote Bag', 'Premium Embroidered Genuine Leather Tote Bag', 'Premium Embroidered Genuine Leather Tote Bag', 'eTIGORk28lhmmrovyDT9Ay14P5NSB5E0qry2hTpl', '2019-09-27 16:21:09', '2019-09-08 10:25:13'),
(24, 'exclusive-artificial-kundan-jewellery-set-6770-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"11\"]', 2, 'JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6770', 'Exclusive Artificial Kundan Jewellery Set [6770]', '18', '6770', '5d7caa7f99750IMG_6770.JPG', '[\"5d7caa7f999c4IMG_6772.JPG\",\"5d7caa7f99b5dIMG_6773.JPG\",\"5d7caa7f99efdIMG_6774.JPG\"]', '<p>Fashioned after antique ethnic jewellery&nbsp;designs, the necklace set, embellished with stones, has been handcrafted. Wear this with a saree and look gorgeous!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Female is incomplete without Jewellery. We at Zouple provides the master piece of jewellery which is beautiful and affordable so that every Indian Women can buy this beautiful Indian Jewellery. We add some extra special elements like love, best design, latest fashions and trend to make it best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We, at Zouple, take care of every piece of jewellery so that you don&#39;t spend hours caring for them. But do remember, fashion jewellery lasts longer when kept dry and free of chemicals. Follow this simple rule: Your jewellery should be the last thing you put on and the first thing you take off.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong> Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6770</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Base Meta</strong>l:Brass</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Kundan&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Type</strong>: Necklace and Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>: Handcrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Plated</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Content: One Necklace with Two Earrings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace have two lines of Kundan work with front &amp; rear both side designs. One line of Green Onyx provided in middle of two lines of Kundan work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure.</p>', '<p>Kundan is a traditional form of indian Gemstone Jewellery involving a gem set with a gold foil between the stones and its mount, usually for elaborate necklaces. The method is believed to have originated in the royal courts of Rajasthan and Gujarat. It is one of the older forms of jewellery made and worn in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kundan, also known as<strong> Bikaneri &amp; Jaipuri jewellery,</strong> is a popular variation, wherein enameling with <em>vivid colours and designs is on the reverse, while the kundan setting is in the front.</em> The city of Jaipur in Rajasthan has traditionally been the centre for Kundan jewellery in India.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Artificial Kundan Jewellery Set', 'Exclusive Artificial Kundan Jewellery Set', 'Exclusive Artificial Kundan Jewellery Set', 'eTIGORk28lhmmrovyDT9Ay14P5NSB5E0qry2hTpl', '2019-09-27 16:20:28', '2019-09-12 11:47:38'),
(25, 'exclusive-artificial-polki-jewellery-set-6776-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"11\"]', 2, 'JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6776', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki Jewellery Set [6776]', '18', '6776', '5d7a36bcd7f9bIMG_6776.JPG', '[\"5d7a36bcd8295IMG_6776.JPG\",\"5d7a36bcd848dIMG_6777.JPG\",\"5d7a36bcd863bIMG_6778.JPG\",\"5d7a36bcd8810IMG_6779.JPG\"]', '<p>The centuries old legacy is carried forward in contemporary polki jewellery designs and has become a new trousseau archetype, treated as the most accomplished fusion of artisanship and design. An impeccably skilled hand is a requisite to work upon&nbsp; polki designer jewellery and produce masterpieces of timeless vintage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This art is relentlessly carried on to complete only one article of jewellery. An elaborate enamelling work is usually seen on the reverse of every traditional Polki artefact, involving hundreds of man-hours, exhibiting an extravagance of sophistication.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6776</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Base Meta</strong>l:Brass</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Polki with Chid Moti&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Type</strong>: Necklace and Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>: Handcrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Plated</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Content: One Necklace with Two Earrings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace have Polki Design with Chid Moti.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure.</p>', '<p>Kundan and Polki are both stones. Polki jewellery is made of unfinished natural diamonds. Polki is essentially an uncut diamond that is mined from the earth in a natural way without any enhancement or lab creation.&nbsp; Polki is always in great demand and highly valued because of its natural form. It is also much shinier and much more expensive than Kundan jewellery.&nbsp; Kundan is made of glass stone (glass polki).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Polki was introduced in India by the Moghuls, while Kundan is a traditional Rajasthani style of jewellery.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'INACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki Jewellery Set', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki Jewellery Set', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki Jewellery Set', 'pjdlbhMJo4qGL7rbIh2ph6NiBxo7mrBVdyWuJL8K', '2019-10-05 17:47:45', '2019-09-12 12:12:32'),
