n with Moti, Zercon, Red Onyx.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure.</p>', '<p>Kundan and Polki are both stones. Polki jewellery is made of unfinished natural diamonds. Polki is essentially an uncut diamond that is mined from the earth in a natural way without any enhancement or lab creation.&nbsp; Polki is always in great demand and highly valued because of its natural form. It is also much shinier and much more expensive than Kundan jewellery.&nbsp; Kundan is made of glass stone (glass polki).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Polki was introduced in India by the Moghuls, while Kundan is a traditional Rajasthani style of jewellery.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'INACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki & Kundan Mix Jewellery Set [6780]', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki & Kundan Mix Jewellery Set [6780]', 'Exclusive Artificial Polki & Kundan Mix Jewellery Set [6780]', 'pjdlbhMJo4qGL7rbIh2ph6NiBxo7mrBVdyWuJL8K', '2019-10-05 17:47:20', '2019-09-14 08:04:54'),
