(31, 'exclusive-multi-tourmaline-polki-jewellery-set-6803-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"11\"]', 2, 'JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6803', 'Exclusive Multi Tourmaline Polki Jewellery Set [6803]', '3', '6803', 'IMG_6803 - Copy.JPG', '[\"IMG_6803.JPG\",\"IMG_6804.JPG\",\"IMG_6805.JPG\"]', '<p>Jewellery is a popular piece of item and loved by every woman that can either be used for personal use or for giving away as a gift.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The centuries old legacy is carried forward in contemporary polki jewellery designs and has become a new trousseau archetype, treated as the most accomplished fusion of artisanship and design. An impeccably skilled hand is a requisite to work upon&nbsp; polki designer jewellery and produce masterpieces of timeless vintage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This art is relentlessly carried on to complete only one article of jewellery. An elaborate enamelling work is usually seen on the reverse of every traditional Polki artefact, involving hundreds of man-hours, exhibiting an extravagance of sophistication.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6803</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Base Meta</strong>l:Brass</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Polki &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Type</strong>: Necklace and Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>: Handcrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Plated</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Additional:</strong>Multi Tourmaline, Moti</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Necklace with Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace have Polki Design with Multi Tourmaline &amp; Moti</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure</p>', '<p>Kundan and Polki are both stones. Polki jewellery is made of unfinished natural diamonds. Polki is essentially an uncut diamond that is mined from the earth in a natural way without any enhancement or lab creation.&nbsp; Polki is always in great demand and highly valued because of its natural form. It is also much shinier and much more expensive than Kundan jewellery.&nbsp; Kundan is made of glass stone (glass polki).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Polki was introduced in India by the Moghuls, while Kundan is a traditional Rajasthani style of jewellery.</p>', 'YES', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Multi Tourmaline Polki Jewellery Set', 'Exclusive Multi Tourmaline Polki Jewellery Set', 'Exclusive Multi Tourmaline Polki Jewellery Set', '4pcbv1Cog6auyyd8tyZluBxuLgNv3rLSJGLMBdP5', '2020-02-07 16:25:42', '2019-09-14 11:52:40'),
(32, 'gold-plated-antique-classic-kundan-earring-7784-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"17\"]', 2, 'JFER-JAG-12/8-ER7784', 'Gold-Plated Antique Classic Kundan Earring [7784]', '3', '7784', '5d7cdd070c6cdIMG_7784.JPG', '[\"5d7cdd070c960IMG_7784.JPG\",\"5d7cdd070cb5eIMG_7786.JPG\",\"5d7cdd070ce27IMG_7787.JPG\",\"5d7cdd070d00cIMG_7788.JPG\",\"5d7cdd070d1e0IMG_7789.JPG\"]', '<p>Gold-Plated antique classic earrings, has kundan secured with a post and back.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code:JFER-JAG-12/8-ER7784</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Gender</strong>: Female</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Kundan &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>Type</strong>:&nbsp; Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>:Antique &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Polish</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong> Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Wipe with a clean cotton swab when needed .</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Kundan Earring [7784]', 'Kundan Earring [7784]', 'Kundan Earring [7784]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 18:07:09', '2019-09-14 12:28:55'),
