(53, 'exclusive-handmade-applique-cutwork-bedsheet-139bs8997', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 3, 'HU-ICB-13/9BS8997', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork  Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', '12', '13/9BS8997', '5d7f827f14c4fIMG_8997.jpg', '[\"5d7f827f1507eIMG_8998.JPG\",\"5d7f827f15522IMG_8999.JPG\",\"5d7f827f15a93IMG_9002.jpg\",\"5d7f827f15e4eIMG_9006.JPG\",\"5d7f827f16193IMG_9007.JPG\",\"5d7f827f16579IMG_9009.JPG\",\"5d7f827f16aa3IMG_9010.JPG\",\"5d7f827f16f1aIMG_9014.jpg\"]', '<p>Exhibit your love for art by decorating your beds with these Applique Cutwork bed sheets. Elegant and attractive, they hug the bed perfectly and sport a wide range of prints and sizes. Made of fine-quality material, these bed sheets are durable and great for regular use. A one stop-shop for handicraft, Zouple sells a product every 30 seconds. So go ahead and buy with confidence.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ICB-13/9BS8997</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong>&nbsp;Applique Cutwork, Orange</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp;1 Bedsheet</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong>&nbsp;Cotton</p>', '<p><strong>Appliqu&eacute;</strong> is ornamental <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Needlework\">needlework</a> in which pieces of fabric in different shapes and patterns are sewn or stuck onto a larger piece to form a picture or pattern. It is commonly used as decoration, especially on garments. The technique is accomplished either by hand or machine. Appliqu&eacute; is commonly practised with <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Textile\">textiles</a>, but the term may be applied to similar techniques used on different materials.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork  Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork  Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork  Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', 'G43bSYkqmRTND2iQj8V4KQY8KvmtGqJnQxOB6RM3', '2019-09-29 17:39:16', '2019-09-16 12:39:27'),
(54, 'exclusive-handmade-applique-cutwork-bedsheet-139bs9016', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 3, 'HU-ICB-13/9BS9016', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork Bedsheet [13/9BS9016]', '12', '13/9BS9016', '5d7f86e29bd3aIMG_9016.jpg', '[\"5d7f86e29c086IMG_9016.jpg\",\"5d7f86e29c374IMG_9017.JPG\",\"5d7f86e29c6bbIMG_9018.JPG\",\"5d7f86e29ca32IMG_9021.jpg\"]', '<p>Exhibit your love for art by decorating your beds with these Applique Cutwork bed sheets. Elegant and attractive, they hug the bed perfectly and sport a wide range of prints and sizes. Made of fine-quality material, these bed sheets are durable and great for regular use. A one stop-shop for handicraft, Zouple sells a product every 30 seconds. So go ahead and buy with confidence.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ICB-13/9BS9016</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong>&nbsp;Applique Cutwork, White</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp;1 Bedsheet</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong>&nbsp;Cotton</p>', '<p><strong>Appliqu&eacute;</strong>&nbsp;is ornamental&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Needlework\">needlework</a>&nbsp;in which pieces of fabric in different shapes and patterns are sewn or stuck onto a larger piece to form a picture or pattern. It is commonly used as decoration, especially on garments. The technique is accomplished either by hand or machine. Appliqu&eacute; is commonly practised with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Textile\">textiles</a>, but the term may be applied to similar techniques used on different materials.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork Bedsheet [13/9BS9016]', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork Bedsheet [13/9BS9016]', 'Exclusive Handmade Applique Cutwork Bedsheet [13/9BS9016]', 'G43bSYkqmRTND2iQj8V4KQY8KvmtGqJnQxOB6RM3', '2019-09-29 17:39:18', '2019-09-16 12:58:10');
