(55, 'exclusive-handmade-embroidery-raw-silk-bedsheet-139bs9026-1', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 3, 'HU-ICB-13/9BS9026', 'Exclusive Handmade Embroidery Raw Silk Bedsheet [13/9BS9026]', '12', '9026', '5d7f8a5ece370IMG_9025.jpg', '[\"5d7f8a5ece760IMG_9025.jpg\",\"5d7f8a5eceac7IMG_9026.JPG\",\"5d7f8a5eceebaIMG_9027.JPG\",\"5d7f8a5ecf3dbUntitled-1.jpg\"]', '<p>Exhibit your love for art by decorating your beds with these Embroidery Raw Silk bed sheets. Elegant and attractive, they hug the bed perfectly and sport a wide range of prints and sizes. Made of fine-quality material, these bed sheets are durable and great for regular use. A one stop-shop for handicraft, Zouple sells a product every 30 seconds. So go ahead and buy with confidence.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ICB-13/9BS9026</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong> Embroidery Work on White Raw Silk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp; 1 Bedsheet with 2 Pillow &amp; 2 Cushion Cover</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong> Raw Silk</p>', '<p><strong>Silk</strong> containing sericin is called <strong>raw silk</strong>. The gummy substance, affording protection during processing, is usually retained until the yarn or fabric stage and is removed by boiling the <strong>silk</strong> in soap and water, leaving it soft and lustrous, with weight reduced by as much as 30 percent.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Handmade Embroidery Raw Silk Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', 'Exclusive Handmade Embroidery Raw Silk Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', 'Exclusive Handmade Embroidery Raw Silk Bedsheet [13/9BS8997]', 'G43bSYkqmRTND2iQj8V4KQY8KvmtGqJnQxOB6RM3', '2019-09-29 17:39:21', '2019-09-16 13:13:02'),
