(75, 'hand-block-bagru-print-cotton-bed-sheet139bs9245', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 3, 'HU-ICB-13/9BS9245', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9245]', '12', '13/9BS9245', '5d8077e4dd68cIMG_9245.JPG', '[\"5d8077e4ddc01IMG_9245.JPG\",\"5d8077e4de0a0IMG_9247.JPG\",\"5d8077e4de622IMG_9248.JPG\",\"5d8077e4dec47IMG_9253.JPG\"]', '<p>Our Bed sheets is designed in such a way that it complement the color and pattern of your space giving you a warm feel at your home. Crafted with happiness, our sheet provides a soft and a comfortable feel to your skin moreover our sheet is anti allergic.A bed sheet which was a necessity in your bedroom is now considered as a matter of aesthetic appeal. The quality, softness and its antiallergic properties are what makes this fabric unmatched.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A one stop-shop for handicraft, Zouple sells a product every 30 seconds. So go ahead and buy with confidence.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ICB-13/9BS9245</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong> Red Border</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp;1 Bedsheet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong>&nbsp;Cotton</p>', '<p><strong>Bagru</strong> is a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/City\">city</a> and a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Municipality\">municipality</a> in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jaipur_district\">Jaipur district</a> Tehsil Sanganer in the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/States_and_territories_of_India\">state</a> of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rajasthan\">Rajasthan</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/India\">India</a>. Bagru is known for <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_dye\">natural dyes</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woodblock_printing_on_textiles\">hand block printing</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Woodblock printing on textiles</strong> is the process of printing patterns on textiles, usually of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linen\">linen</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cotton\">cotton</a> or <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silk\">silk</a>, by means of incised <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wood\">wooden</a> blocks. It is the earliest, simplest and slowest of all methods of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Textile_printing\">textile printing</a>. Block printing by hand is a slow process. It is, however, capable of yielding highly artistic results, some of which are unobtainable by any other method.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9245]', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9245]', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9245]', 'G43bSYkqmRTND2iQj8V4KQY8KvmtGqJnQxOB6RM3', '2019-09-29 18:12:48', '2019-09-17 06:06:28'),
(76, 'hand-block-bagru-print-cotton-bed-sheet-139bs9255', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 3, 'HU-ICB-13/9BS9255', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet [13/9BS9255]', '12', '13/9BS9255', '5d807baaaa14fIMG_9254.JPG', '[\"5d807baaaa6e4IMG_9254.JPG\",\"5d807baaaabc8IMG_9256.JPG\",\"5d807baaab1b5IMG_9257.JPG\",\"5d807baaab8afUntitled-1.jpg\"]', '<p>Our Bed sheets is designed in such a way that it complement the color and pattern of your space giving you a warm feel at your home. Crafted with happiness, our sheet provides a soft and a comfortable feel to your skin moreover our sheet is anti allergic.A bed sheet which was a necessity in your bedroom is now considered as a matter of aesthetic appeal. The quality, softness and its antiallergic properties are what makes this fabric unmatched.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A one stop-shop for handicraft, Zouple sells a product every 30 seconds. So go ahead and buy with confidence.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ICB-13/9BS9255</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong>&nbsp;Red Border</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp;1 Bedsheet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong>&nbsp;Cotton</p>', '<p><strong>Bagru</strong>&nbsp;is a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/City\">city</a>&nbsp;and a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Municipality\">municipality</a>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jaipur_district\">Jaipur district</a>&nbsp;Tehsil Sanganer in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/States_and_territories_of_India\">state</a>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rajasthan\">Rajasthan</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/India\">India</a>. Bagru is known for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_dye\">natural dyes</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woodblock_printing_on_textiles\">hand block printing</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Woodblock printing on textiles</strong>&nbsp;is the process of printing patterns on textiles, usually of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linen\">linen</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cotton\">cotton</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silk\">silk</a>, by means of incised&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wood\">wooden</a>&nbsp;blocks. It is the earliest, simplest and slowest of all methods of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Textile_printing\">textile printing</a>. Block printing by hand is a slow process. It is, however, capable of yielding highly artistic results, some of which are unobtainable by any other method.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9255]', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9255]', 'Hand Block Bagru Print Cotton Bed Sheet[13/9BS9255]', 'G43bSYkqmRTND2iQj8V4KQY8KvmtGqJnQxOB6RM3', '2019-09-29 18:12:51', '2019-09-17 06:22:34'),
