(104, 'premium-embroidered-cotton-bedsheet-139bs9715-1', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 1, 'HU-ZPL-13/9BS9715', 'Premium Embroidered Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9715]', '12', '9715', '5d80eb63721c7IMG_9715.JPG', '[\"5d80eb6372725IMG_9715.JPG\",\"5d80eb6372bbcIMG_9716.JPG\",\"5d80eb63730b7IMG_9717.JPG\",\"5d80eb6373510IMG_9718.JPG\",\"5d80eb6373a05IMG_9719.JPG\",\"5d80eb6373fdeIMG_9723.JPG\"]', '<p>Give a premium touch to your bedroom with this bedsheet. The vibrant embroidery on the bedsheet will give a simple yet classy feel to your bedroom.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ZPL-13/9BS9715</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong>&nbsp;Multicolour</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp;1 Bedsheet, 2 Pillow cover</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong>&nbsp;Cotton</p>', '<p>Embroidered Block Print Cotton Bedsheet</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Premium Embroidered Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9715]', 'Premium Embroidered Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9715]', 'Premium Embroidered Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9715]', 'pjdlbhMJo4qGL7rbIh2ph6NiBxo7mrBVdyWuJL8K', '2019-10-05 13:08:22', '2019-09-17 14:19:15'),
(105, 'premium-printed-kantha-work-cotton-bedsheet-139bs9726', 0, '[\"2\",\"6\"]', 1, 'HU-ZPL-13/9BS9726', 'Premium Printed & Kantha Work Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9726]', '12', '9726', '5d80ec9dc8570IMG_9726.JPG', '[\"5d80ec9dc89ccIMG_9726.JPG\",\"5d80ec9dc8d2aIMG_9728.JPG\",\"5d80ec9dc915cIMG_9729.JPG\",\"5d80ec9dc9581IMG_9742.JPG\"]', '<p>Our Bed sheets is designed in such a way that it complement the color and pattern of your space giving you a warm feel at your home. Crafted with happiness, our sheet provides a soft and a comfortable feel to your skin moreover our sheet is anti allergic.A bed sheet which was a necessity in your bedroom is now considered as a matter of aesthetic appeal. The quality, softness and its antiallergic properties are what makes this fabric unmatched.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A one stop-shop for handicraft, Zouple sells a product every 30 seconds. So go ahead and buy with confidence.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand: Zouple</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CODE: HU-ZPL-13/9BS9726</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Colour:</strong> Red Print &amp; Kantha Work</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Set Content:</strong>&nbsp;1 Bedsheet</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Weight(Approx):</strong>&nbsp;1 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong>&nbsp;Cotton</p>', '<p>Printed &amp; Kantha Work Cotton Bedsheet</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Premium Printed & Kantha Work Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9726]', 'Premium Printed & Kantha Work Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9726]', 'Premium Printed & Kantha Work Cotton Bedsheet [13/9BS9726]', 'pjdlbhMJo4qGL7rbIh2ph6NiBxo7mrBVdyWuJL8K', '2019-10-05 13:06:56', '2019-09-17 14:24:29'),
(106, 'exclusive-polki-jewellery-set-6806', 0, '[\"3\",\"11\"]', 2, 'JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6806', 'Exclusive Polki Jewellery Set [6806]', '3', '11/8N6806', '5d81ce9ef3f04IMG_6806.JPG', '[\"5d81ce9ef41b9IMG_6806.JPG\",\"5d81ce9f0017cIMG_6807.JPG\",\"5d81ce9f00386IMG_6808.JPG\"]', '<p>Jewellery is a popular piece of item and loved by every woman that can either be used for personal use or for giving away as a gift.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The centuries old legacy is carried forward in contemporary polki jewellery designs and has become a new trousseau archetype, treated as the most accomplished fusion of artisanship and design. An impeccably skilled hand is a requisite to work upon&nbsp; polki designer jewellery and produce masterpieces of timeless vintage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This art is relentlessly carried on to complete only one article of jewellery. An elaborate enamelling work is usually seen on the reverse of every traditional Polki artefact, involving hundreds of man-hours, exhibiting an extravagance of sophistication.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6806</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Polki &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Type</strong>: Necklace and Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>: Handcrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Plated</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Additional:</strong>Chid Moti</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Necklace with Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace have Polki Design Chid Moti</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure</p>', '<p>Kundan and Polki are both stones. Polki jewellery is made of unfinished natural diamonds. Polki is essentially an uncut diamond that is mined from the earth in a natural way without any enhancement or lab creation.&nbsp; Polki is always in great demand and highly valued because of its natural form. It is also much shinier and much more expensive than Kundan jewellery.&nbsp; Kundan is made of glass stone (glass polki).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Polki was introduced in India by the Moghuls, while Kundan is a traditional Rajasthani style of jewellery.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Polki Jewellery Set [6806]', 'Exclusive Polki Jewellery Set [6806]', 'Exclusive Polki Jewellery Set [6806]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 18:10:46', '2019-09-18 06:28:47'),
(107, 'premium-pacchikari-pendent-set-118n6811-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"11\"]', 2, 'JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6811', 'Premium Pacchikari Pendent Set [11/8N6811]', '3', '6811', '5d81d199d0830IMG_6809.JPG', '[\"5d81d199d0aa5IMG_6809.JPG\",\"5d81d199d0c6aIMG_6810.JPG\",\"5d81d199d0e32IMG_6811.JPG\"]', '<p>Jewellery is a popular piece of item and loved by every woman that can either be used for personal use or for giving away as a gift.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Female is incomplete without Jewellery. We at Zouple provides the master piece of jewellery which is beautiful and affordable so that every Indian Women can buy this beautiful Indian Jewellery. We add some extra special elements like love, best design, latest fashions and trend to make it best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We, at Zouple, take care of every piece of jewellery so that you don&#39;t spend hours caring for them. But do remember, fashion jewellery lasts longer when kept dry and free of chemicals. Follow this simple rule: Your jewellery should be the last thing you put on and the first thing you take off.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-WI-JAG-11/8N6811</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Base Meta</strong>l:Brass</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Style</strong>: Pacchikari &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Type</strong>: Necklace and Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>: Handcrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Plated