ellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>Wipe with a clean cotton swab when needed</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Gold Polished Carving Bali [14/8ER8103]', 'Gold Polished Carving Bali [14/8ER8103]', 'Gold Polished Carving Bali [14/8ER8103]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 19:55:46', '2019-09-18 18:14:11'),
(174, 'gold-plated-meenakari-kundan-earring-8110-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"17\"]', 2, 'JFER-JAG-14/8ER8110', 'Gold-Plated Meenakari & Kundan Earring [8110]', '3', '8110', '5d8276c9f1fadIMG_8113.JPG', '[\"5d8276c9f21eeIMG_8108.JPG\",\"5d8276c9f23a9IMG_8110.JPG\",\"5d8276c9f2612IMG_8111.JPG\",\"5d8276c9f27bfIMG_8112.JPG\"]', '<p>Gold-Plated Meenakari &amp; Kundan Earring with post &amp; back Closing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Female is incomplete without Jewellery. We at Zouple provides the master piece of jewellery which is beautiful and affordable so that every Indian Women can buy this beautiful Indian Jewellery. We add some extra special elements like love, best design, latest fashions and trend to make it best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JFER-JAG-14/8ER8110</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Gender</strong>: Female</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>:Meenakari &amp; Kundan &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Type</strong>:&nbsp; Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>:Antique &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Meenakari Art:&nbsp;</strong>Meenakari is an age old art form of decorating metal with colored enamel. It is reputed for its excellent designs and beautiful colour combinations.The artisans who practice this art form are called &lsquo;Meenakars&rsquo;. The art form mainly involves making colorful jewellery. Other objects produced using Meenakari include, decorative articles, arm chairs, dining sets, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The art form has its origin in Persia. It was prevalent in the Mughal palaces. Raja Man Singh of Amber invited skilled Meenakars from the Mughal palace at Lahore to Jaipur. He brought this art to Rajasthan. Now, Jaipur is a renowned centre for Meenakari art form.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Gold-Plated Meenakari & Kundan Earring [8110]', 'Gold-Plated Meenakari & Kundan Earring [8110]', 'Gold-Plated Meenakari & Kundan Earring [8110]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 19:56:59', '2019-09-18 18:26:17'),
