(206, 'amathyst-chalcidony-mala-52-faces-148sm8336-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8336', 'Amathyst & Chalcidony Mala, 52 Faces [14/8SM8336]', '3', '8336', '5d82ae6e5c538IMG_8337.JPG', '[\"5d82ae6e5c7fdIMG_8335.JPG\",\"5d82ae6e5c9fbIMG_8336.JPG\",\"5d82ae6e5cbecIMG_8338.JPG\",\"5d82ae6e5cde5IMG_8339.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Amathyst &amp; Chalcidony mala with 52 faces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chalcedony </strong>protects against negative influences,&nbsp;this gemstone increases energy and brings emotional balance. Chalcedony comes in many different colors including white, blue, gray, green, yellow, red, brown, pink, purple, and black. Each color activates healing from a different level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chalcedony heals by warding off negative energy such as hostility and sadness, it boosts confidence and stimulates enthusiasm. This &ldquo;Stone of Generosity&rdquo; encourages kindness, understanding, unity, and brotherhood.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amethyst</strong> has healing powers to help with physical ailments, emotional issues, and in Energy Healing and Chakra balancing. <strong>Amethyst crystal</strong> therapies are primarily associated with physical ailments of the nervous system, the curing of nightmares and insomnia, and balancing the crown chakra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8336</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: Amathyst &amp; Chalcidony, 52 Faces</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Amathyst & Chalcidony Mala [14/8SM8336]', 'Amathyst & Chalcidony Mala [14/8SM8336]', 'Amathyst & Chalcidony Mala [14/8SM8336]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:33:49', '2019-09-18 22:23:42'),
