(217, 'black-onyx-mala-52-faces-148sm8399-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8399', 'Black Onyx Mala, 52 Faces [14/8SM8399]', '3', '8399', '5d82bd76682b5IMG_8398.JPG', '[\"5d82bd76684e4IMG_8400.JPG\",\"5d82bd7668783IMG_8401.JPG\",\"5d82bd7668a49IMG_8402.JPG\",\"5d82bd7668c87IMG_8403.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Black Onyx mala with 52 faces on each stone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits of Black Onyx:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A powerful protection stone, Black Onyx absorbs and transforms negative energy, and helps to prevent the drain of personal energy. Black Onyx aids the development of emotional and physical strength and stamina, especially when support is needed during times of stress, confusion or grief. Black Onyx fosters wise decision-making.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse Black Onyx to encourage happiness and good fortune. Black Onyx is a strength-giving stone and can provide support for self-discipline issues. Because it helps to hold physical memories, Black Onyx can be useful in healing old wounds or past life issues.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBlack Onyx is wonderful for meditation and dreaming. When using Black Onyx for either of these purposes, it is recommended to use a secondary grounding stone in combination with the Onyx. Black Onyx helps one to become master of their own future.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8399</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone:Black Onyx, 52 Faces</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Black Onyx Mala [14/8SM8399]', 'Black Onyx Mala [14/8SM8399]', 'Black Onyx Mala [14/8SM8399]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:40:55', '2019-09-18 23:27:50'),
(218, 'turquoise-mala-148sm8405-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8405', 'Turquoise Mala [14/8SM8405]', '3', '8405', '5d82be64276c8IMG_8404.JPG', '[\"5d82be6427903IMG_8404.JPG\",\"5d82be6427a8dIMG_8405.JPG\",\"5d82be6427cdeIMG_8406.JPG\",\"5d82be6427f2aIMG_8407.JPG\",\"5d82be6428185IMG_8408.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Turquoise Mala.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>It is a perfect companion for those who travel a lot. It protects them from thefts, accidents, or any unwanted incidences.</li>\r\n	<li>Turquoise drives good luck in wearer&#39;s life.</li>\r\n	<li>Turquoise helps in maintaining stability and concord in married life by infusing deep understanding in partners.</li>\r\n	<li>It liberates one from negative energies</li>\r\n	<li>It enhances one spiritual state of awareness to help one getter better connected with the true physical and spiritual world.</li>\r\n	<li>Those suffering from asthma, depression, dental problems, excessive alcoholism, high blood pressure, infections, poison, radiation, or toxins can overcome their impact with the help of this stone</li>\r\n	<li>Panic attacks, frequent tiredness, and problems of low energy levels can also be eliminated with it.</li>\r\n	<li>Turquoise is considered a pure stone. Hence, it saves the wearer from mishaps and violence while also reducing mental stress.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8405</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: Turquoise</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Turquoise Mala [14/8SM8405]', 'Turquoise Mala [14/8SM8405]', 'Turquoise Mala [14/8SM8405]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:41:34', '2019-09-18 23:31:48'),
(219, 'chalcidony-mala-52-faces-148sm8410-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8410', 'Chalcidony Mala, 52 Faces [14/8SM8410]', '3', '8410', '5d82bf43ad573IMG_8409.JPG', '[\"5d82bf43ad86aIMG_8409.JPG\",\"5d82bf43adaabIMG_8410.JPG\",\"5d82bf43add5eIMG_8411.JPG\",\"5d82bf43ae014IMG_8412.JPG\",\"5d82bf43ae243IMG_8413.JPG\"]', '<p>A elegant Chalcidony mala with 52 faces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chalcedony protects against negative influences,&nbsp;this gemstone increases energy and brings emotional balance. Chalcedony comes in many different colors including white, blue, gray, green, yellow, red, brown, pink, purple, and black. Each color activates healing from a different level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chalcedony heals by warding off negative energy such as hostility and sadness, it boosts confidence and stimulates enthusiasm. This <strong>&ldquo;Stone of Generosity&rdquo;</strong> encourages kindness, understanding, unity, and brotherhood.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code:</strong> <strong>JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8410</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: Chalcidony, 52 Faces</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Chalcidony Mala, 52 Faces [14/8SM8410]', 'Chalcidony Mala, 52 Faces [14/8SM8410]', 'Chalcidony Mala, 52 Faces [14/8SM8410]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:41:52', '2019-09-18 23:35:31'),
