(233, 'german-silver-victorian-earring-208er8649-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"17\"]', 2, 'JFER-JAG-20/8ER8649', 'German Silver Victorian Earring [20/8ER8649]', '3', '8649', '5d833bff49cfcIMG_8651.JPG', '[\"5d833bff4a00fIMG_8649.JPG\",\"5d833bff4a1baIMG_8651.JPG\",\"5d833bff4a40aIMG_8652.JPG\",\"5d833bff4a5b0IMG_8653.JPG\",\"5d833bff4a751IMG_8654.JPG\"]', '<p>German Silver Earring with Post &amp; Back closing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;re looking to add a touch of grace and elegance to your day, we think this German Silver Earring would be perfect for the job!</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>JFER-JAG-20/8ER8649</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Gender</strong>: Female</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>:German Silver&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Type</strong>:&nbsp; Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>:Antique &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>Wipe with a clean cotton swab when needed</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'German Silver Victorian Earring [20/8ER8649]', 'German Silver Victorian Earring [20/8ER8649]', 'German Silver Victorian Earring [20/8ER8649]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:43:06', '2019-09-19 08:27:43'),
(235, 'gold-plated-antique-classic-kundan-earring-208er8665-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"17\"]', 2, 'JFER-JAG-20/8ER8665', 'Gold-Plated Antique Classic Kundan Earring [20/8ER8665]', '3', '8665', '5d833eed7c842IMG_8665.JPG', '[\"5d833eed7ca8bIMG_8665.JPG\",\"5d833eed7cc26IMG_8666.JPG\",\"5d833eed7ceb2IMG_8667.JPG\",\"5d833eed7d060IMG_8668.JPG\"]', '<p>Gold-Plated antique classic earrings, has kundan secured with a post and back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Female is incomplete without Jewellery. We at Zouple provides the master piece of jewellery which is beautiful and affordable so that every Indian Women can buy this beautiful Indian Jewellery. We add some extra special elements like love, best design, latest fashions and trend to make it best.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JFER-JAG-20/8ER8665</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Gender</strong>: Female</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Kundan &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Type</strong>:&nbsp; Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>:Antique &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Polish</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>Kundan is a traditional form of indian Gemstone Jewellery involving a gem set with a gold foil between the stones and its mount, usually for elaborate necklaces. The method is believed to have originated in the royal courts of Rajasthan and Gujarat. It is one of the older forms of jewellery made and worn in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kundan, also known as<strong>&nbsp;Bikaneri &amp; Jaipuri jewellery,</strong>&nbsp;is a popular variation, wherein enameling with&nbsp;<em>vivid colours and designs is on the reverse, while the kundan setting is in the front.</em>&nbsp;The city of Jaipur in Rajasthan has traditionally been the centre for Kundan jewellery in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Gold-Plated Antique Classic Kundan Earring [20/8ER8665]', 'Gold-Plated Antique Classic Kundan Earring [20/8ER8665]', 'Gold-Plated Antique Classic Kundan Earring [20/8ER8665]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:43:10', '2019-09-19 08:40:13');
