(259, 'exclusive-decorative-marble-elephant-set-118e7208-1', 0, '[\"2\",\"7\"]', 2, 'HAC-JAG-11/8E7208', 'Exclusive Decorative Marble Elephant Set [11/8E7208]', '12', '7208', '5d83da59d0a0dIMG_7209.JPG', '[\"5d83da59d0d19IMG_7205.JPG\",\"5d83da59d0f13IMG_7206.JPG\",\"5d83da59d1102IMG_7207.JPG\",\"5d83da59d12ccIMG_7208.JPG\",\"5d83da59d1470IMG_7209.JPG\",\"5d83da59d16adIMG_7210.JPG\"]', '<p>Surprisingly elegant and beautiful Marble Elephant Set for decorative purpose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It can be used anywhere in your drawing room, bed room or kids room or office/shop to increase the beauty of place.</p>', '<p>Brand: Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code:&nbsp;HAC-JAG-11/8E7208</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material</strong>:Marble, Set of Two Elephant</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Size:</strong>&nbsp;Please select a size</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Purpose:</strong>&nbsp;Decoration</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trend:&nbsp;</strong>Handicraft</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Decorative Marble Elephant Set.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Two Colours are available i.e.Brown &amp; Blue. Product may be delivered as per availibility. It will be confirmed before delivery.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Decorative Marble Elephant Set [11/8E7208]', 'Exclusive Decorative Marble Elephant Set [11/8E7208]', 'Exclusive Decorative Marble Elephant Set [11/8E7208]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 22:38:41', '2019-09-19 19:43:21'),
(260, 'exclusive-kundan-jewellery-set-with-green-onyx-zircon-118n7064', 0, '[\"3\",\"11\"]', 2, 'JAJ-EI-JAG-11/8N7064', 'Exclusive Kundan Jewellery Set with Green Onyx & Zircon [11/8N7064]', '3', '7064', '5d83e758cc937IMG_7065.JPG', '[\"5d83e758ccf3eIMG_7064.JPG\",\"5d83e758cd339IMG_7065.JPG\",\"5d83e758cd96eIMG_7066.JPG\",\"5d83e758cddc3IMG_7067.JPG\"]', '<p>Fashioned after antique ethnic jewellery&nbsp;designs, the necklace set, embellished with stones, has been handcrafted. Wear this with a matching saree and look gorgeous!</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-EI-JAG-11/8N7064</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stone Type</strong>: Kundan&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp; Type</strong>: Necklace and Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends</strong>: Handcrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; Plating</strong>: Gold-Plated</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Content: One Necklace with Two Earrings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure.</p>', '<p>Kundan is a traditional form of indian Gemstone Jewellery involving a gem set with a gold foil between the stones and its mount, usually for elaborate necklaces. The method is believed to have originated in the royal courts of Rajasthan and Gujarat. It is one of the older forms of jewellery made and worn in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kundan, also known as<strong>&nbsp;Bikaneri &amp; Jaipuri jewellery,</strong>&nbsp;is a popular variation, wherein enameling with&nbsp;<em>vivid colours and designs is on the reverse, while the kundan setting is in the front.</em>&nbsp;The city of Jaipur in Rajasthan has traditionally been the centre for Kundan jewellery in India.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Kundan Jewellery Set with Green Onyx & Zircon [11/8N7064]', 'Exclusive Kundan Jewellery Set with Green Onyx & Zircon [11/8N7064]', 'Exclusive Kundan Jewellery Set with Green Onyx & Zircon [11/8N7064]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:47:56', '2019-09-19 20:38:48'),
(261, 'green-onyx-mala-set-5-lines-118sm7061-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7061', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7061]', '3', '7061', '5d83e944c745eIMG_7060.JPG', '[\"5d83e944c76f8IMG_7060.JPG\",\"5d83e944c7901IMG_7061.JPG\",\"5d83e944c7ca1IMG_7062.JPG\",\"5d83e944c7eb5IMG_7063.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Green Onyx mala set in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The word Onyx originates from the Greek term &lsquo;onux&rsquo;, meaning claw or fingernail. As the bands on the stone represent colors of a nail, the stone has been named so. While usually, the stone is black in color, you can also find pink, red, brown and even green onyx gemstones. You can even find colorless onyx gemstones. It is a popular substitute for Emerald Gemstone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Like Emerald, Onyx is also very helpful to strengthen the positive powers of Mercury planet.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7061</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Stone: Green Onyx, 5 Lines</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Gold plated Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala &amp; Two Earrings</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7061]', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7061]', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7061]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:48:00', '2019-09-19 20:47:00'),
(262, 'red-onyx-mala-set-5-lines-118sm7056-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7056', 'Red Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7056]', '3', '7056', '5d83ea5d8d2b5IMG_7056.JPG', '[\"5d83ea5d8d54aIMG_7056.JPG\",\"5d83ea5d8d758IMG_7057.JPG\",\"5d83ea5d8daadIMG_7058.JPG\",\"5d83ea5d8dccdIMG_7059.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful 5 lines Red Oyx mala set.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Red Onyx is related to your Root Chakra. It has the healing meanings that are inherent to any colour of Onyx. Onyx is strength-giving, providing support in difficult or confusing times, as well as during times of enormous mental or physical stress.&nbsp; Some of its other healing properties include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Centers your energy &amp; aligns it with a higher power, helping you to access higher guidance</li>\r\n	<li>Imparts personal strength and helps you to be master of your destiny</li>\r\n	<li>Promotes vigor, steadfastness and stamina</li>\r\n	<li>Helps you in learning lessons</li>\r\n	<li>Gives you self-confidence</li>\r\n	<li>Helps you to be at ease in your surroundings</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7056</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: Red Onyx, 5 </strong><strong>Lines</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Gold Plated Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala &amp; 2 Earring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Red Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7056]', 'Red Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7056]', 'Red Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7056]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:48:02', '2019-09-19 20:51:41'),
(263, 'exclusive-african-amathyst-mala-5-lines-118sm7052-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7052', 'Exclusive African Amathyst Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7052]', '3', '7052', '5d83eb76dbf95IMG_7052.JPG', '[\"5d83eb76dc414IMG_7051.JPG\",\"5d83eb76dc6c5IMG_7052.JPG\",\"5d83eb76dca6aIMG_7053.JPG\",\"5d83eb76dccf0IMG_7054.JPG\",\"5d83eb76dcfa2IMG_7055.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Amathyst mala in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.Cell-Growth Promotion: Far-Infrared radiation is known to promote cell-growth and cell-regeneration.Scientific studies have shown that by increasing the infrared radiation level in your body,you will have more energy to grow &amp; regrow cells in your Body.The benefit of far-infrared radiation is that its wavelengths are very long,but enough to provide them with life-giving energy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.Sleeping Aid: The low level of heat emitted by Amethyst crystals can help to calm your body, and help you sleep.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.Blood-Circulation Enhancement</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.Better Circulation of Bodily Fluids: Blood is not the only bodily fluid whose motility or circulation ability is increased by far -infrared radiation.Far-infrared radiation increases the flexibility of your blood vessels generally speaking,as a result,everything in the body reaches its destination more quickly. It also helps to speed up your overall fluid transportation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5.Increased Anti-Oxidant Activity<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6.Healing Power for Wounds: Far infrared radiation helps to repair tissue that is damaged as a result of diabetes mellitus,reconstructive surgeries or other chronic and acute damage.Prevention of the Follwing Diseasea:-Paralysis,Astma,Teeth Problmes, any Bones-Problems,Nerves,Harmonic Gland,Spinalcord-Diseases.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n7.The Benefits of Amethyst Generated Negative Ion Emission,Negative Ions are free electrons or any simple molecule with a net negative charge.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n8.Enhancing Respiration<br />\r\n<br />\r\n9.Amethyst Protects the Warer from Unexpected Happenings and Natural Calamitis and Ensures Greater Financial Stability.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n10.People Feel Happier<br />\r\n<br />\r\n11.Amethyst Help also Govern Perfection,Wisdom,Intergrity,Spiritual Achievement,Humility,Patience,Higest Human Qualities,Long Life,Denials,Misery,Adversity.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n12.Amethyst also Protects the Wearers against Risks of Accidents and against the Dangers of Fire,Strom &amp; Natural Calamites.Amethyst Should Reflectpure Colour,Be Homogenous and Soft to Touch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmethyst Mainly Work for Saturn Planet with works of Stabilizes Mind,Source of Courage and Luck,Brings Love &amp; Harmony,Important Things to Remember, Healing Properties,Liberates From Addictions,tendency to help,spiritual growth,It is also believed to be a conqueror of all bad habits which calls for crossing limits to arrive at extremities of the wrong end.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7052</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: African Amathyst, 5 Lines</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive African Amathyst Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7052]', 'Exclusive African Amathyst Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7052]', 'Exclusive African Amathyst Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7052]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:48:56', '2019-09-19 20:56:22'),
(264, 'premium-rainbow-mala-yellow-blue-sapphire-emerald-ruby-5-lines-118sm7047-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7047', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 5 Lines [11/8SM7047]', '3', '7047', '5d83ecf51d7d9IMG_7049.JPG', '[\"5d83ecf51db10IMG_7047.JPG\",\"5d83ecf51dd88IMG_7048.JPG\",\"5d83ecf51e0a6IMG_7049.JPG\",\"5d83ecf51e2e7IMG_7050.JPG\"]', '<p>A gorgeous rainbow multistone mala in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The powers of a&nbsp;<strong>yellow sapphire</strong>&nbsp;protect its wearer from an accidental death. Provides mental peace, courage and happiness.&nbsp;<strong>Yellow Sapphire</strong>&nbsp;reduces one&#39;s tendency of getting angry. Jupiter is the most benefic planet and by wearing a&nbsp;<strong>yellow sapphire</strong>&nbsp;gemstone, its malefic effects are completely negated.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The result is a good gain of self-confidence and mental balance. Surprisingly,&nbsp;<strong>blue sapphire</strong>&nbsp;also has some health&nbsp;<strong>benefits</strong>. Wearing the Neelam/<strong>Blue Sapphire</strong>&nbsp;aids in digestion too. It also helps prevent several stomach related ailments in the individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People having issues retaining wealth can&nbsp;<strong>benefit</strong>&nbsp;by&nbsp;<strong>emerald</strong>&nbsp;stone, as it is said to have the power to hold money with the wearer. Children who cannot concentrate on their work and studies can&nbsp;<strong>benefit</strong>&nbsp;from&nbsp;<strong>emerald</strong>&nbsp;stone as well, as it increases concentration in individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ruby</strong>&nbsp;gemstone will support a person to achieve name, fame, popularity and build their desired carrier. It helps to increase creativity and self-confidence in wearer&#39;s life. As per Indian astrology, the&nbsp;<strong>ruby</strong>&nbsp;gemstones depict the naval Chakra of the human body and help in removing the fear and depression.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7047</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: </strong>Yellow &amp; Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 5 Lines [11/8SM7047]', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 5 Lines [11/8SM7047]', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 5 Lines [11/8SM7047]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 21:59:03', '2019-09-19 21:02:45');
