(265, 'blue-onyx-mala-5-lines-118sm7044-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7044', 'Blue Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7044]', '3', '7044', '5d83ee23128ecIMG_7044.JPG', '[\"5d83ee2312c0eIMG_7042.JPG\",\"5d83ee2312e05IMG_7044.JPG\",\"5d83ee2313071IMG_7045.JPG\",\"5d83ee2313224IMG_7046.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Blue Onyx mala in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <strong>blue onyx</strong> is a gem, which may increase your own contentment and happiness in life. It may also enhance your intuition, as well as strengthen your resolve in changing your bad habits. It is also a strength giving gem, which may be good for those who are always under great emotional, physical, or mental stress.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7044</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: </strong>Blue Onyx, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Blue Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7044]', 'Blue Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7044]', 'Blue Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7044]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:51:22', '2019-09-19 21:07:47'),
(267, 'green-onyx-mala-5-lines-118sm7035', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7035', 'Green Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7035]', '3', '7035', '5d83f05566d09IMG_7033.JPG', '[\"5d83f05566fb4IMG_7033.JPG\",\"5d83f0556719cIMG_7034.JPG\",\"5d83f05567414IMG_7035.JPG\",\"5d83f0556763cIMG_7036.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Green Onyx mala in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The word Onyx originates from the Greek term &lsquo;onux&rsquo;, meaning claw or fingernail. As the bands on the stone represent colors of a nail, the stone has been named so. While usually, the stone is black in color, you can also find pink, red, brown and even green onyx gemstones. You can even find colorless onyx gemstones. It is a popular substitute for Emerald Gemstone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Like Emerald, Onyx is also very helpful to strengthen the positive powers of Mercury planet.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7035</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: </strong>Green Onyx, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7035]', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7035]', 'Green Onyx Mala Set, 5 Lines [11/8SM7035]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:51:28', '2019-09-19 21:17:09'),
(268, 'premium-rainbow-mala-yellow-blue-sapphire-emerald-ruby-8-lines-118sm7029-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7029', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 8 Lines [11/8SM7029]', '3', '7029', 'IMG_7029 - Copy.JPG', '[\"IMG_7029.JPG\",\"IMG_7030.JPG\",\"IMG_7031.JPG\",\"IMG_7032.JPG\"]', '<p>A gorgeous rainbow multistone mala in 8 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The powers of a <strong>yellow sapphire</strong> protect its wearer from an accidental death. Provides mental peace, courage and happiness. <strong>Yellow Sapphire</strong> reduces one&#39;s tendency of getting angry. Jupiter is the most benefic planet and by wearing a <strong>yellow sapphire</strong> gemstone, its malefic effects are completely negated.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The result is a good gain of self-confidence and mental balance. Surprisingly, <strong>blue sapphire</strong> also has some health <strong>benefits</strong>. Wearing the Neelam/<strong>Blue Sapphire</strong> aids in digestion too. It also helps prevent several stomach related ailments in the individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People having issues retaining wealth can <strong>benefit</strong> by <strong>emerald</strong> stone, as it is said to have the power to hold money with the wearer. Children who cannot concentrate on their work and studies can <strong>benefit</strong> from <strong>emerald</strong> stone as well, as it increases concentration in individuals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ruby</strong> gemstone will support a person to achieve name, fame, popularity and build their desired carrier. It helps to increase creativity and self-confidence in wearer&#39;s life. As per Indian astrology, the <strong>ruby</strong> gemstones depict the naval Chakra of the human body and help in removing the fear and depression.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7029</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone:&nbsp;</strong>Yellow &amp; Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 8 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'YES', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 8 Lines [11/8SM7029]', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 8 Lines [11/8SM7029]', 'Premium Rainbow Mala-Yellow & Blue Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby, 8 Lines [11/8SM7029]', '4pcbv1Cog6auyyd8tyZluBxuLgNv3rLSJGLMBdP5', '2020-02-07 16:32:58', '2019-09-19 21:22:00'),
(269, 'coraline-mala-5-lines-118sm7026-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7026', 'Coraline Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7026]', '3', '7026', '5d83f2712e494IMG_7025.JPG', '[\"5d83f2712e8faIMG_7025.JPG\",\"5d83f2712ec98IMG_7026.JPG\",\"5d83f2712f0b0IMG_7027.JPG\",\"5d83f2712f2f1IMG_7028.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful 5 lines Coraline mala.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7026</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: Coraline</strong>, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Coraline Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7026]', 'Coraline Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7026]', 'Coraline Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7026]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:51:36', '2019-09-19 21:26:09'),
(270, 'black-onyx-mala-5-lines-118sm7022-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7022', 'Black Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7022]', '3', '7022', '5d83f3dda71b1IMG_7021.JPG', '[\"5d83f3dda7495IMG_7021.JPG\",\"5d83f3dda7693IMG_7022.JPG\",\"5d83f3dda7867IMG_7023.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Black Onyx mala in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits of Black Onyx:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A powerful protection stone, Black Onyx absorbs and transforms negative energy, and helps to prevent the drain of personal energy. Black Onyx aids the development of emotional and physical strength and stamina, especially when support is needed during times of stress, confusion or grief. Black Onyx fosters wise decision-making.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse Black Onyx to encourage happiness and good fortune. Black Onyx is a strength-giving stone and can provide support for self-discipline issues. Because it helps to hold physical memories, Black Onyx can be useful in healing old wounds or past life issues.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBlack Onyx is wonderful for meditation and dreaming. When using Black Onyx for either of these purposes, it is recommended to use a secondary grounding stone in combination with the Onyx. Black Onyx helps one to become master of their own future.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7022</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: </strong>Black Onyx, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Black Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7022]', 'Black Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7022]', 'Black Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7022]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:56:32', '2019-09-19 21:32:13'),
(271, 'yellow-chalcedony-mala-5-lines-118sm7018-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7018', 'Yellow Chalcedony Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7018]', '3', '7018', '5d83f4f38aa67IMG_7017.JPG', '[\"5d83f4f38ad5aIMG_7017.JPG\",\"5d83f4f38af95IMG_7018.JPG\",\"5d83f4f38b238IMG_7019.JPG\",\"5d83f4f38b46aIMG_7020.JPG\"]', '<p>Yellow beauty in Chalcedony formed in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yellow Chalcedony promotes the ability to implement positive changes. It enhances harmony, positivity, joy, and peace. This refreshing gemstone encourages you to appreciate the life you have and to live in the present moment. Yellow Chalcedony is a <em>&quot;Stone of Optimism.&quot;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chalcedony protects against negative influences,&nbsp;increases energy and promotes emotional balance. It absorbs negativity and dissipates it, allowing you to feel the warmth of inner-stability and self-assurance.&nbsp;It wards off feelings of hostility and sadness, boosting confidence and enthusiasm. Chalcedony brings balance to your mind, body, and emotions. This powerful healer assists those who lack maternal instincts, and lessens the effects of dementia and senility.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7018</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone:&nbsp;</strong>Yellow Chalcedony, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Yellow Chalcedony Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7018]', 'Yellow Chalcedony Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7018]', 'Yellow Chalcedony Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7018]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:56:36', '2019-09-19 21:36:51'),
(272, 'red-onyx-mala-5-lines-118sm7014-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7014', 'Red Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7014]', '3', '7014', '5d83f5ec6a81bIMG_7013.JPG', '[\"5d83f5ec6aa87IMG_7013.JPG\",\"5d83f5ec6ac6fIMG_7014.JPG\",\"5d83f5ec6aed4IMG_7015.JPG\",\"5d83f5ec6b0a0IMG_7016.JPG\"]', '<p>A beautiful Red Onyx mala in 5 lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Red Onyx is related to your Root Chakra. It has the healing meanings that are inherent to any colour of Onyx. Onyx is strength-giving, providing support in difficult or confusing times, as well as during times of enormous mental or physical stress.&nbsp; Some of its other healing properties include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Centers your energy &amp; aligns it with a higher power, helping you to access higher guidance</li>\r\n	<li>Imparts personal strength and helps you to be master of your destiny</li>\r\n	<li>Promotes vigor, steadfastness and stamina</li>\r\n	<li>Helps you in learning lessons</li>\r\n	<li>Gives you self-confidence</li>\r\n	<li>Helps you to be at ease in your surroundings</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-11/8SM7014</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Stone: Red Onyx</strong>, 5 Lines&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Mala&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Mala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Red Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7014]', 'Red Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7014]', 'Red Onyx Mala, 5 Lines [11/8SM7014]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 20:56:40', '2019-09-19 21:41:00'),
