aline handmade mala in 4 lines.</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive Tourmaline Mala, 4 Lines [11/8SM7005]', 'Exclusive Tourmaline Mala, 4 Lines [11/8SM7005]', 'Exclusive Tourmaline Mala, 4 Lines [11/8SM7005]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 21:00:26', '2019-09-19 21:55:06'),
