(358, 'embroidered-cotton-kurta-298k0292-1', 0, '[\"18\",\"19\"]', 3, 'WFC-ICB-29/8K0292', 'Embroidered Cotton Kurta [29/8K0292]', '12', '0292', '5d87962a0f7dcUntitled-11111.jpg', '[\"5d87962a0faceUntitled-1.jpg\",\"5d87962a0fcfcUntitled-11.jpg\",\"5d87962a0ff1cUntitled-111.jpg\",\"5d87962a1038fUntitled-11111.jpg\"]', '<p>You&#39;ll love the style, comfort and durability of this Embroidery kurta. Dress up for your next family event by pairing this gorgeous piece with your best simple jewellery.</p>', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"height:180px; width:384px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Category</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Mix &amp; Match</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Fit</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Long</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Colour/Design</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Embroidery</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Neckline</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Round Collar</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Fabric</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Cotton</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Sleeve</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Short Sleeve</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Content</strong></td>\r\n			<td>1 Kurta</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Code</strong></td>\r\n			<td>WFC-ICB-29/8K0292</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Hand Wash Cold,Wash Like Colors Separately,Tumble Dry Low,Do Not Bleach,Medium Iron/ Do Not Iron Direct</p>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Embroidered Cotton Kurta [29/8K0292]', 'Embroidered Cotton Kurta [29/8K0292]', 'Embroidered Cotton Kurta [29/8K0292]', 'G43bSYkqmRTND2iQj8V4KQY8KvmtGqJnQxOB6RM3', '2019-09-29 19:09:34', '2019-09-22 15:41:30'),
(359, 'american-diamond-bangles-with-green-red-onyx-128b7522-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"12\"]', 2, 'JIB-JAG-12/8B7522', 'American Diamond Bangles with Green & Red Onyx [12/8B7522]', '3', '7522', '5d88774be1dd8IMG_7529.jpg', '[\"5d88774be1fc7IMG_7521.jpg\",\"5d88774be213fIMG_7522.jpg\",\"5d88774be243dIMG_7524.jpg\",\"5d88774be2654IMG_7525.jpg\",\"5d88774be2855IMG_7527.jpg\"]', '<p>Look your absolute best every time you head out wearing these bangles. Wear this pair with an ethnic or fusion attire to add grace to your appearance.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:&nbsp;</strong>Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JIB-JAG-12/8B7522</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Pattern:&nbsp;</strong>American Diamond<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Size:&nbsp;</strong>2.4, 2.6, 2.8 (As per selection)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends:</strong>&nbsp;Handicraft&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;2 Bangles</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'American Diamond Bangles with Carving Work [12/8B7522]', 'American Diamond Bangles with Carving Work [12/8B7522]', 'American Diamond Bangles with Carving Work [12/8B7522]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 21:38:07', '2019-09-23 07:42:03'),
(360, 'machine-cut-lac-bangle-in-red-chid-moti-128b7531-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"12\"]', 2, 'JIB-JAG-12/8B7531', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Red Chid Moti [12/8B7531]', '3', '7531', '5d887f9c2a8caIMG_7534.jpg', '[\"5d887f9c2ae2bIMG_7530.jpg\",\"5d887f9c2b064IMG_7531.jpg\",\"5d887f9c2b3c1IMG_7532.jpg\",\"5d887f9c2b5e9IMG_7535.jpg\",\"5d887f9c2b825IMG_7536.jpg\"]', '<p>Every Female is incomplete without Jewellery. We at Zouple provides the master piece of jewellery which is beautiful and affordable so that every Indian Women can buy this beautiful Indian Jewellery. We add some extra special elements like love, best design, latest fashions and trend to make it best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We, at Zouple, take care of every piece of jewellery so that you don&#39;t spend hours caring for them. But do remember, fashion jewellery lasts longer when kept dry and free of chemicals. Follow this simple rule: Your jewellery should be the last thing you put on and the first thing you take off.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:&nbsp;</strong>Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JIB-JAG-12/8B7531</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Pattern: </strong>Lac Bangles<strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; <strong>Size:&nbsp;</strong>2.4, 2.6, 2.8 (As per selection)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends:</strong>&nbsp;Handicraft&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Metal/Plating</strong>: 9k one gram gold polish</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;2 Bangles &amp; 2 Chudis</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Red Chid Moti [12/8B7531]', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Red Chid Moti [12/8B7531]', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Red Chid Moti [12/8B7531]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 21:38:16', '2019-09-23 07:51:20'),
(361, 'machine-cut-lac-bangle-in-crystal-128b7538-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"12\"]', 2, 'JIB-JAG-12/8B7538', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Crystal [12/8B7538]', '3', '7538', '5d88806981030IMG_7538.jpg', '[\"5d8880698146eIMG_7537.jpg\",\"5d88806981691IMG_7539.jpg\",\"5d8880698190cIMG_7541.jpg\",\"5d88806981be5IMG_7542.jpg\",\"5d88806981e90IMG_7543.jpg\"]', '<p>Whether you love classic, traditional styles or desire a contemporary, fusion look, bangles can help make your outfit stand out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;re looking to add a touch of grace and elegance to your day, we think this Lac Bangles with crystal would be perfect for the job!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:&nbsp;</strong>Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JIB-JAG-12/8B7538</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Pattern:&nbsp;</strong>Lac Bangles<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Size:&nbsp;</strong>2.4, 2.6, 2.8 (As per selection)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends:</strong>&nbsp;Handicraft&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Metal/Plating</strong>: 9k one gram gold polish</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;2 Bangles &amp; 2 Chudis</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Crystal [12/8B7538]', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Crystal [12/8B7538]', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in Crystal [12/8B7538]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8zJ1GFkJwnRkzMx0FDOytb7vQ', '2019-09-28 21:38:20', '2019-09-23 08:20:57'),
