(379, 'machine-cut-lac-bangle-in-white-chid-moti-128b7672-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"12\"]', 2, 'JIB-JAG-12/8B7672', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in White Chid Moti [12/8B7672]', '3', '7672', '5d889c19b5c1dIMG_7672.jpg', '[\"5d889c19b5ee01. zouple bangle size chart.jpg\",\"5d889c19b601bIMG_7671.jpg\",\"5d889c19b62a6IMG_7673.jpg\",\"5d889c19b6514IMG_7675.jpg\",\"5d889c19b67a4IMG_7676.jpg\",\"5d889c19b6a13IMG_7677.jpg\"]', '<p>Whether you love classic, traditional styles or desire a contemporary, fusion look, bangles can help make your outfit stand out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;re looking to add a touch of grace and elegance to your day, we think this Lac Bangles with white chid moti would be perfect for the job!</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:&nbsp;</strong>Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JIB-JAG-12/8B7672</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Pattern:&nbsp;</strong>Lac Bangles<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Size:&nbsp;</strong>2.4, 2.6, 2.8 (As per selection)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Trends:</strong>&nbsp;Handicraft&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Metal/Plating</strong>: 9k one gram gold polish</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;2 Bangles &amp; 2 Chudis</p>', '<p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wipe your jewellery with a soft cloth after every use</li>\r\n	<li>Always store your jewellery in a flat box to avoid accidental scratches</li>\r\n	<li>Keep sprays and perfumes away from your jewellery</li>\r\n	<li>Do not soak your jewellery in water</li>\r\n	<li>Clean your jewellery using a soft brush, dipped in jewellery cleaning solution only</li>\r\n</ul>', 'NO', 'NO', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in White Chid Moti [12/8B7672]', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in White Chid Moti [12/8B7672]', 'Machine Cut Lac Bangle in White Chid Moti [12/8B7672]', 'us7qm8dWCZWEB6v8z