(384, 'exclusive-white-chid-moti-rani-haar-148sm8157-1', 0, '[\"3\",\"13\"]', 2, 'JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8157', 'Exclusive White Chid Moti Rani Haar [14/8SM8157]', '3', '8157', 'IMG_8155 - Copy.jpg', '[\"IMG_8155.jpg\",\"IMG_8156.jpg\",\"IMG_8157.jpg\",\"IMG_8158.JPG\"]', '<p>Rani Haar is gorgeous neckpiece that is worn on special occasions. Rani haar is an occasional jewellery because they are heavier and longer than usual necklaces. They&rsquo;ll make the perfect wedding jewellery for the bride. Moreover, these types of jewellery can also be categorized as heirloom jewellery because they are made up of all things precious and tell a story on one&rsquo;s ancestor which is passed on from one generation to another.</p>', '<p><strong>Brand:</strong>&nbsp;Zouple</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Code: JAJ-JAG-14/8SM8157</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Occasion</strong>:Ethnic&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Style</strong>:Rani Haar&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type</strong>: Necklace&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Trends</strong>: Handicrafted&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Additional:</strong> White Chid Moti</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>Content:</strong>&nbsp;One Necklace</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Necklace is secured with a drawstring closure</p>', '<p>Rani Haar with White Chid Moti</p>', 'YES', 'YES', 'ACTIVE', 'INSTOCK', 'Exclusive White Chid Moti Rani Haar [14/8SM8157]', 'Exclusive White Chid Moti Rani Haar [14/8SM8157]', 'Exclusive White Chid Moti Rani Haar [14/8SM8157]', 'TAMLkLJShRe5RjndbmPWRxjBYy7fYi6OngEzTtJ1', '2020-07-29 08:52:13', '2019-09-23 11:42:21');
