(1, 'The Zouple', NULL, 'Block:E  Mukundpura, Bhankrota Jaipur, Rajasthan PIN:303006', 'contact@thezouple.com', 'The Zouple - Online Shopping Store', 'The Zouple - Online Shopping Store', '<p>Zouple, during its long journey, is dedicated to unite premium and unique accessories to its family with a common passion. It is dedicated to make unique designs that could be available to everybody. We are creating a convenient and inspiring experience for our customers. Our brands engage with customers in online as well as in social media and other creative places. Shopping should be easy and relevant regardless of where, when and how customers choose to shop. We are also developing the presentation and functionalities online while personalising our sites.</p>', 'The Zouple', 'https://www.facebook.com/zouplefashion', 'https://www.linkedin.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/connect_zouple/', 'https://twitter.com/TheZouple', '60', '1', '1', 10, 'Rajasthan', 'India', 'JAIPUR', '0.10', 'https://in.pinterest.com', 'https://youtu.be/fVo9mjOPmvk', 'SNuw66Zz1ODq7cy7euyYbHyESNhVXs4o4QsmQRuh', '2019-03-12 05:55:08', '2020-08-06 11:54:55');
